| 10 | `ios/Yugma/` folder | Rename entire folder |
| 11 | `ios/Yugma.xcodeproj/` | Rename project |
| 12 | [Podfile](file:///Users/vikalpnimesh/Desktop/Matpatra/Y/Yugma/ios/Podfile#L17) | `target 'Yugma'` → new name |
| 13 | `project.pbxproj` | ~40+ references to `Yugma` |

> [!NOTE]
> If you're **only** changing the bundle identifier (e.g., `com.yugmamatch` → `com.newname.yugma`) but keeping the app name as "Yugma", you **don't** need to touch items 10-13.

